Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美紅  英語作業借我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有留作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天感冒請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  我可是指望美紅的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  土宮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做英語作業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  能借來看下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮同學  也借我看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  是郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  醫院來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮的媽媽在住院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  你家煩心事這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:00:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我必須走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本子放在這就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真匆忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課叫你出來不好意思啊  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都對老師撒謊真過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還留著口水的痕跡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的神樂怪臉收藏又多了一張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種收藏最好刪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N「任務之大義」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得最近超自然災害增加了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  惡靈出現次數有些多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉寂了一段時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有三年沒出現這現象了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一根Pocky歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手快者得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴快者得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好  有什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴裡喊著不要也是喜歡的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉這個色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別往這邊看  變態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對不起了  上課時還把你們叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的使命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們  被大叔看就無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩端先生是那方面的喜好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面的就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  櫻庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…臀部長得不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別拿那種眼神看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐正在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類型B  土蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可是巨無霸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鵺迅速解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之  讓管狐退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  請往後退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又是後方支援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你獨擔重任還太早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你把舞蹴拾貳號運用自如了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經駕輕就熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那讓我見識一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始掩護黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咆哮波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮  弄碎它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通市民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  有受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到剛才的東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用拐彎抹角了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是環境省超自然災害對策室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是消除惡靈的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈感強的人容易被惡靈盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的甚至有無法成佛而自身卻變成惡靈的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別再靠近這種地方為好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡所見的千萬別向外透露一句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你寫份誓約書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕生可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我暫時幫你收著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐說這附近已經沒有惡靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  狀況解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道那女人想自殺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全憑經驗囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積累經驗多了自然就會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了便當  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮啊  你媽媽的病很嚴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你真了不起啊  還認真完成了作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍稍忙了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為工作幾乎不怎麼回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在寄宿在親戚家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是超不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能和親戚家的姐姐玩又能幫忙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…親戚家的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  你在打工了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是見習中  幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  能工作就很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No  不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀的保養請使用山茶油或丁香油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是日本人的愛刀之心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這  你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  家裡來了個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  是邁克爾師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來看我們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉啊  好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快問好啊  這樣很失禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是土宮神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是土宮大人的女兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是邁克爾小原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾小原不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是打造這把刀的著名刀匠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹴拾貳號  居然是他造的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策室的裝備也是邁克爾師傅製作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在問你為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀身閃閃發光  跟新的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為都不怎麼讓我作戰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了對神樂來說還為時過早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我看下獅子王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這仍是把好刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那綻放著強大靈力的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時看來就這麼讓人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈力消耗得過多了點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該重新打磨一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子王被拿去打磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時就要在沒有靈獸的情況下戰鬥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都要精心照顧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能召喚靈獸就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來  這種時候就方便多了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見過爸爸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不定時回家見見他的話他會感到很孤單的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家沒關係的  就算回了也沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  我添麻煩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆當我家孩子算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  邁克爾師傅來過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  好像是要暫時保管獅子王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有想給對策室裡需要維修的退魔武器進行保養
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就一起麻煩他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？那樣的話緊急情況發生時裝備就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也該讓她擔任主要戰鬥力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼訓練能比得上實戰的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  一直依賴小亂也不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揀日不如撞日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把輪班調整下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我會去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人為什麼一直都不穿衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死了了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大叔還是這麼累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身打扮還真虧他不會被抓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾還是會被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近段時間可以稍稍休息下了  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是沒了獅子王就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩端先生  讓我看看退魔裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本都拿去維修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的話用這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是電熨斗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式鐵拳打杯28號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（打杯28號：退魔式鐵拳。邁克爾小原製作的退魔武器、通過打擊對靈體產生破壞。）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用靈水蒸汽外加鐵拳  把惡靈打得滿地找牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有能看上眼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式鏈鋸  PARE  11號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式鑿岩機  JACKSON  33號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔式鍋爐  J.FOX  55號這些而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個都差那麼點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這麼重怎麼拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之  陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天有預約了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫某人一直在輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  用這個去練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不陪諫山好嗎  畢竟是未婚妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是讓我去討好父母決定的對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是毫無感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來說照顧現在這個「女兒」就夠受的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不去打擾為妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20的三倍區  中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧得那麼無微不至  真像個「母親」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就要定下妻子啊女兒什麼的  也真夠受的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是15病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（15病：飛鏢瞄準20卻射中1和5的情況）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才趁現在多玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒無所謂  但別每次都拿我當擋箭牌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會被諫山憎恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她憎恨那可是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  的確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算能打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真的有威力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾師傅造的武器可是很優秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據使用者的靈力  其威力也可以提升數倍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂的舞蹴拾貳號也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇形怪狀的也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那人是位藝術家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對策室來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（有封新郵件）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是靈力分佈出現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前銀座線的新橋站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在似乎是作為夜晚停車庫和休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去碰輸電軌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會觸電而死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近惡靈出沒真頻繁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡氣若是積攢起來  被召喚的惡靈就會聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡氣更是愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣惡性循環下去  就成惡靈的聚集之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初惡氣生成一定存在某些原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還蠻好用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類型C  天井嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡混凝土的污垢的惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈水用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個果然不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類型D  惡靈化的人類亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那個人已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是曾經是人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成怨靈的靈只能淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍下去  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們退魔師的使命就是驅除在人世間散佈死亡汙穢之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰靈解放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮家代代相傳最強的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰靈  白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道出生在退魔師家所應擔負的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道這份責任有多重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不斷修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快變強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:26.40,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:37.08,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:47.80,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.79,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:23:00.39,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.79,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:11.06,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:26.55,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:26.40,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經對自己的心靈　許下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:37.08,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救贖　捲入嘆息漩渦中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:47.80,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交錯的時光轉瞬即逝　道理的齒輪鏽跡斑斕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.79,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已經無法後退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:23:00.39,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毀一切　亦無容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.79,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:11.06,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將那時僅有的幸福　深情擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:26.55,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}將遠去的夢的足音　刻骨銘心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  喰霊  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「執念」


